### Which @angular/* package(s) are relevant/related to the feature request?

core

### Description

The effect has to do an Initial run to keep track of the used signal, If we have untracked inside of it it would be nice to skip the Initial run.

### Proposed solution

```typescript
constructor() {
  effect(() => {
      const someSignalValue = this.signalStuff()
      untracked(() => {
         this.doSomethingWithValue(someSignalValue)
      },{skipInitial: true});
    });
}
```

### Alternatives considered

```typescript
constructor() {
let skipInitial = true;
  effect(() => {
      const someSignalValue = this.signalStuff()
      untracked(() => {
         if (skipInitial) {
             skipInitial = false;
             return;
         }
         this.doSomethingWithValue(someSignalValue)
      });
    });
}
```

### Command

serve

